window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jake Anders is the Monster Master, a mage of godlike power who has saved the realm of Elwyn time and again. First from the Void King, then once more from the vile monstrous entity known as Vâ€™galmor.</p> <p>For his efforts, the Elfmother has decided to grant rulership of her realm to him, but she is slain by an assassin shortly after voicing her decision to make Jake her successor.</p> <p>As the reluctant King of the North, Jake Anders must now secure his realm, rally his allies, Capture more Monsters, and heighten his magical prowess, if he wishes to stand a chance at all against the malevolent Empress of the Dark Elves and her mighty army.</p>"; 
